  "title": "Vanilla World",
  "description": "Add vanilla dimensions while keeping the original dimensions.",
  "body": "# Vanilla World\n\nHave you ever thougth of getting overwhelmed while playing with world generation datapack or mod but still want to have it? Have you wanted a sepparate vanilla dimensions that doesn't get affected by datapack or mod? This mod solved it.\n\nVanilla World will add vanilla dimensions while keeping the original dimensions. This mod dimensions will not affected by datapack or mod like TerraBlender (Biomes O' Plenty, Region Unexplored, Oh The Biomes We've Gone, etc), William Wythers' Overhauled Overworld, etc.\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/C_b93AckR4I\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n## Features\n\n- No client needed vanilla world.\n- Include isolated vanilla Overworld, Nether, and The End dimension.\n- Include datapack to change generation mode.\n- Include datapack for alternative portal with coarse dirt corner.\n- Datapack support.\n\n### Generation Mode\n\n- Default: Unmodified Vanilla Biomes.\n- Full Vanilla: Unmodified Vanilla Biomes + Vanilla Terrain Generation.\n- Normal: Vanilla Biomes.\n- Normal Terrain: Vanilla Biomes + Vanilla Terrain Generation.\n\nVanilla Terrain Generation is **experimental** feature to bypass terrain or world generation datapack or mod like Tectonic, Terralith, William Wythers' Expanded Ecosphere, etc.\n\nSuggest new features for vanilla world on [GitHub Discussion](https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-vanillaworld/discussions) or [Discord](https://discord.gg/cuYgFmq3kz) would be appreciated.\n\n## Usage\n\nTo access Vanilla World, make portal with obsidian frame and dirt on the frame corner like this:\n\n![Vanilla World Portal](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9ffbcb91ace0ef20f4278c3344dd77d18d1f1ed4.jpeg)\n\n## Compatibility\n\n- Default or Normal Mode:\n  - Tectonic\n  - Terralith\n  - William Wythers' Expanded Ecosphere\n- Normal or Normal Terrain Mode:\n  - Geophilic\n- [Passengers Portal Fix](https://modrinth.com/project/LI0BrUQA)\n- **Create** Addons: [Create: Portal Integration](https://modrinth.com/project/2f4ngcAb)\n\n## Issues\n\nThere are no new compatibility issues or bugs being reported. Please report it on [GitHub](https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-vanillaworld/issues) so it can be fixed. Make sure to check the dependencies first.\n\n## Support\n\n🟨 26.1-26.1.2 / 🟩 1.21.1 / 🟥 1.21 / 🟩 1.20.1 / 🟪 1.16.5 / 🟪 1.12.2\n\n🟩 Supported  \n🟥 Support Dropped  \n🟨 In Progress  \n🟪 Considered  \n\n## Important Note\n\nFeel free to use in modpacks, videos, stream, or similar media. Consider help me financially if you like this mod, I will be really grateful.\n\n<br />\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/social/github-plural_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"See me on GitHub\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/mahmudindes\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/available/curseforge_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Available on CurseForge\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@oreno69\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/social/youtube-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Watch me on YouTube\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/cuYgFmq3kz\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/social/discord-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Chat with me on Discord\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://patreon.com/mahmudindes\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/donate/patreon-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/oreno\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/donate/kofi-singular-alt_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://saweria.co/mahmudindes\"><img src=\"https://github.com/barraIhsan/devins-badges/blob/saweria/assets/compact-minimal/donate/saweria-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Support me on Saweria\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/hJmXo78w\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-dimensionfixer/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/dimensionfixer/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Dimension Fixer\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/mgRpdg8r\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-dimensionlink/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/dimensionlink/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Dimension Link\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/A2PZGios\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-worldportal/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/worldportal/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"World Portal\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/cs5vil9i\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-morecatvariants/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/morecatvariants/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"More Cat Variants\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/LI0BrUQA\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-passengersportalfix/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/passengersportalfix/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Passengers Portal Fix\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/2f4ngcAb\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-createportalintegration/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/createportalintegration/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Create Portal Integration\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/8SpfTsnq\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-superflatdimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/superflatdimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Superflat Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/y4wxFDPW\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-amplifieddimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/amplifieddimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Amplified Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/Fo9Xodfg\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-largebiomesdimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/largebiomesdimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Large Biomes Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/Y3EdVfom\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-mushroomfieldsdimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/mushroomfieldsdimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Mushroom Fields Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/ItO3yfpJ\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-beta173dimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/beta173dimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Beta 1.7.3 Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/HkbFed4W\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-desertdimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/desertdimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Desert Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/HW5SOOxi\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-badlandsbiomesdimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/badlandsbiomesdimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Badlands Biomes Dimension\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/63pdCQ3Y\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-forestbiomesdimension/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/forestbiomesdimension/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Forest Biomes